text: Cheang Chon Man (born June 22, 1971) is a Macau professional football player and manager. He plays as a striker for clubs G.D. Negro Rubro, PSP Macau, G.D. Lam Pak and Hong Ngai. Since 2012 he is a coach of the PSP Macau. ==Honours== *Macau Championship: 2 :: 2005, 2006 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Macau footballers Category:Macau international footballers Category:G.D.
